              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9794974287942163507"> A lush and complex book that is thoroughly entertaining. I could recommend this for anyone, Steven King fans should also consider it. This is rich in folklore, even covers a good bit of Beowolf. I classify this as a mystery/thriller. With each detail added to the story, the mystery increases.</span>

